nodes.text: "Unseen Planets of Episode I" is an article written by Daniel Wallace and illustrated by Chris Trevas that appeared in Star Wars Insider 56. It features four planets (Neimoidia, Tund, Malastare, and Iego) that were mentioned but not seen in Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace.
This article follows "The Unseen Planets of Star Wars" in Insider 36 and is followed by "The Unseen Planets of Episode II" in Insider 80.
